Menstrual Phase (Days 1-5): Shedding of the uterine lining (menstruation);
Follicular Phase (Days 1-13): Development and maturation of the ovarian follicle in response to FSH;
Ovulation (Day 14): Release of the mature egg from the ovary in response to the LH surge;
Luteal Phase (Days 15-28): Formation of the corpus luteum and secretion of progesterone to prepare the uterus for potential implantation.
